    "According to the output value from fuzzy, it will be decided to delete the image or remain it for more extra time which is predetermined previously.",
    "The proposed application can be implemented in any smart device such as smartphones, tablets, etc.",
    "When the application captures a photo of the kid, it can detect his feeling as shown in Fig. 3.",
    "The Emotion Detection Assistant (EDA) Application can be active in the background while the child uses another application.",
    "EDA is used to detect the emotion of the kid."
